The third incarnation of [[United States|American]] toy company [[Hasbro]]'s '''[[My Little Pony]]''' [[Toy|toyline]] and [[media franchise]] began in 2003. The revamped line of dolls was targeted to a younger audience than the previous lines.<ref>{{cite news|title=Hasbro Revamps My Little Pony to Draw Younger Girls|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-105890012.html|accessdate=9 August 2014|work=Marketing Week|date=10 July 2003}}</ref> This particular era is often unofficially referred to as "Generation Three" or "G3" by collectors. Until the generation's end in 2009, there have been at least two minor revamps. A series of direct-to-video animated films (mostly produced by [[SD Entertainment]]) accompanied the line-up.

==Toys==
{{Infobox toy
|name       = My Little Pony
|image      =
